text: Emanuel Davidson (19 August 1902 - 3 November 1955) was a Dutch diver. He competed in the men's 10 metre platform event at the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1902 births Category:1955 deaths Category:Dutch male divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
